Author Contributions
Z. Z. designed and performed experiments, conducted device fabrication and measurements, analysed data
and wrote of the paper. H.Z. contributed in material fabrication and electrochemical measurements of carbon
foam using different thicknesses. Y.Z. contributed to BET experimental measurements and its analysis. H. Q.
helped in manuscript correction and device performance analysis. A.G. helped in the Li-ion batteries fabrication
and manuscript correction. R.N. helped in Raman and XRD analysis. H.E. contributed in the analysis of EIS
data. A.L.S. explained the role of electrode thickness in Li-ion batteries. H.L. helped in manuscript correction
and electrochemical analysis. S.C. contributed in material fabrication and characterization and some valuable
suggestions for the electrochemical measurements. Q.Q. helped manuscript correction, providing timely valuable
suggestion and financial support for the overall project.
